room_title: Escape room "The Detective's Office" by Escape House Fargo in Fargo
room_description: The well known and respected, Detective Miggy, is nowhere to be found. He brought four different suspects into custody for the murder of Brenda Jones. The Chief and the whole department is turning to you for help before the case is turned over to internal affairs. Do you have what it takes to locate the evidence and exonerate suspects?
